><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534276\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534276\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 15, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104yum1665703178203.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yum1665703178203.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yum1665703178203.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"yum1665703178203\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Parses a list of items consisting of Name=Value pairs.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"yum1665703178203__topic_d132515e1_d132516e1_d132517e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yum1665703178203__p_d132518e1_d132519e1_d132520e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">int GetItem(unsigned char *<var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var>, unsigned char **<var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var>, int *<var class=\"keyword varname\">NameLen</var>, unsigned char **<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>, unsigned char **<var class=\"keyword varname\">Next</var>)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yum1665703178203__section_w3790ab1b5b3_w3791ab1b5_w3792ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d511598e73\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__1\"> Type </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__2\"> Name </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__3\"> Direction </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__4\"> Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__1\"> unsigned char * </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__3\"> IN </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__4\"> List to build </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__1\"> unsigned char * </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__3\"> INOUT </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__4\"> Name of item </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__1\"> int * </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">NameLen</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__3\"> OUT </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__4\"> Length of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__1\"> unsigned char ** </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__3\"> OUT </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__4\"> Value of item </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__1\"> unsigned char ** </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Next</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__3\"> OUT </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15785e1_d15786e1_d15787e1__entry__4\">Pointer to next location;\n                    <code class=\"ph codeph\">*<var class=\"keyword varname\">Next</var>\n</code> should be zero on the first call. The caller should not change the value. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yum1665703178203__section_w3793ab1b5b5_w3794ab1b5_w3795ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d511598e214\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15788e1_d15789e1_d15790e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15788e1_d15789e1_d15790e1__entry__1\"> Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15788e1_d15789e1_d15790e1__entry__2\"> Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15788e1_d15789e1_d15790e1__entry__1\"> 0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15788e1_d15789e1_d15790e1__entry__2\"> Value not found </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15788e1_d15789e1_d15790e1__entry__1\"> &gt;0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yum1665703178203__table_d15788e1_d15789e1_d15790e1__entry__2\"> Length of list </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yum1665703178203__section_w3796ab1b5b7_w3797ab1b5_w3798ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d511598e263\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yum1665703178203__p_d132530e1_d132531e1_d132532e1\">This function parses a list of items in which items\n        are separated by a byte with the value 27, 0x1b. Items are pairs in the form\n          <var class=\"keyword varname\">Name=Value</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yum1665703178203__p_d132533e1_d132534e1_d132535e1\">Given the name and value, the function returns a\n        pointer to the value and its length.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yum1665703178203__p_d132536e1_d132537e1_d132538e1\">The function can be used to walk through a list if the\n        name is NULL. If <code class=\"ph codeph\">*next</code> is NULL, it starts at the specified\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">list</code>; otherwise it starts at the next unused item. The caller should save\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">*next</code> or the start of the list, as this is the current name for which\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">namelen</code> is returned.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yum1665703178203__p_d132539e1_d132540e1_d132541e1\">The list names and values may be in UTF-8. Separators\n        such as <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> and space are in ASCII.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">In the following example, <code class=\"ph codeph\">GetItem</code> is being used to retrieve information\n        from a list of parameters: </p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104yum1665703178203_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"yum1665703178203__codeblock_fpd_nn1_fwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">DrvArea-&gt;User = DrvArea-&gt;Buffer + total;\n   len = GetItem(parameters, (USTRING*)\"USER\", &amp;namelen, &amp;value, &amp;next);\n   ustrncpy (DrvArea-&gt;User, value, len);\n   total += len;\n   DrvArea-&gt;Buffer[total++] = CHAR_EOS;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tdi1665703178578.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>PutItem</a><p>Builds a list of Name=Value pairs.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534276\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534276\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "GetItem Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 15, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Parses a list of items consisting of Name=Value pairs. int GetItem(unsigned char * List , unsigned char ** Name , int * NameLen , unsigned char ** Value , unsigned char ** Next ) Parameters Type Name Direction Description unsigned char * List IN List to build unsigned char * Name INOUT Name of item int * NameLen OUT Length of Name unsigned char ** Value OUT Value of item unsigned char ** Next OUT Pointer to next location; * Next should be zero on the first call. The caller should not change the value. Return Values Value Description 0 Value not found >0 Length of list Description This function parses a list of items in which items are separated by a byte with the value 27, 0x1b. Items are pairs in the form Name=Value . Given the name and value, the function returns a pointer to the value and its length. The function can be used to walk through a list if the name is NULL. If *next is NULL, it starts at the specified list ; otherwise it starts at the next unused item. The caller should save *next or the start of the list, as this is the current name for which namelen is returned. The list names and values may be in UTF-8. Separators such as = and space are in ASCII. In the following example, GetItem is being used to retrieve information from a list of parameters: Explain this code DrvArea->User = DrvArea->Buffer + total; len = GetItem(parameters, (USTRING*)\"USER\", &namelen, &value, &next); ustrncpy (DrvArea->User, value, len); total += len; DrvArea->Buffer[total++] = CHAR_EOS; Copy Related Links PutItem Builds a list of Name=Value pairs. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}